---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro"

import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro"

import changelogImage from "../assets/changelog.jpg"

import { Image } from "astro:assets"
import Link from "../components/Link.astro"
import ChangelogEntry from "../components/changelog/ChangelogEntry.astro"
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Changelog | Rafa Audibert"
  description="Rafa Audibert's Changelog"
>
  <div class="stack gap-20 mb-4">
    <main class="wrapper changelog">
      <Hero
        title="Changelog"
        tagline="A timeline of what's going on in my life."
      >
        <Image
          src={changelogImage}
          alt="Rafa Audibert and his beautiful fiancée at the top of the Montreal Ferris Wheel looking at the marina and the bridge behind it"
          class="hero-image"
        />

        {
          /* This is written during build time which means it'll be updated on deploy only */
        }
        <div class="last-updated-note">
          Last updated: {
            new Date().toLocaleDateString("en-US", {
              month: "long",
              day: "numeric",
              year: "numeric",
            })
          }
        </div>
      </Hero>

      <!-- =========== 2025 =========== -->
      <ChangelogEntry year={2025} month="August">
        <p>
          Posthog Analytics super-team offsite in Barcelona 🇪🇸! It was nice
          going back to my favourite city in Spain. Amazing colleagues doing
          amazing work + great chill time with superb Catalan food.
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <ChangelogEntry month="July">
        <p>
          Eurotrip 🇪🇺 with Lili. We visited Milan and Sardinia 🇮🇹, Edimburgh and
          London 🇬🇧. <br />
          Had a blast, never knew these places were so beautiful, would go back to
          all of them. Might make sense to spend more time in <Link
            href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/WCdLSeF7ok6Fdg4a9"
            >Isola Madalena</Link
          > next time.
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <ChangelogEntry month="May">
        <p>
          Spent a week in beautiful Florida 🇺🇸 with my fiancée. <br />
          We visited Disney's EPCOT and Holywood Studios parks in Orlando. <br
          />
          We then rented a convertible Mustang GT - check that off my bucket list
          ✅ - and drove to West Palm Beach and Miami 🌞.
        </p>
        <p>
          Attended my first PostHog offsite in Tulum, Mexico 🇲🇽. I worked on a
          new Link Tracking product as part of our Hackathon, but also enjoyed
          some chill time on the beautiful Caribbean Sea (and heated pool 🏊🏻).
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <ChangelogEntry month="April">
        <p>
          First experience in an all-inclusive resort in Punta Cana, 🇩🇴! <br />
          I'm not a heavy-drinker, but we made good use of the restaurants and room-service
          at 3 AM 🥓🥖🍔
        </p>
        <p>
          Started venue-hunting for our wedding, we've decided we'll marry in
          the <Link href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/UyNKMaEwgDLYNXSS7"
            >Vale dos Vinhedos</Link
          > region, just outside our home town 💒
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <ChangelogEntry month="March">
        <p>
          Started my own product at PostHog: <Link
            href="https://posthog.com/teams/revenue-analytics"
            >Revenue Analytics</Link
          > 💰
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <ChangelogEntry month="February">
        <p>
          I'm 25 now! First birthday in years that I wasnt traveling and had the
          chance to spend it with my family!
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <!-- =========== 2024 =========== -->
      <ChangelogEntry year={2024} month="November">
        <p>
          Started working at <Link href="https://posthog.com">PostHog</Link> 🦔,
          one of my dream jobs. I'm working on the Web Analytics team for now.
        </p>
        <p>Visited my team in London 🇬🇧.</p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <ChangelogEntry month="October">
        <p>I got engaged 💍 to my beautiful fiancée, Liliane Basso.</p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <ChangelogEntry month="July">
        <p>
          3-week trip of a lifetime to the East Coast of the United States 🇺🇸.
          New York City 🗽, Washington D.C. 🕴🏻, Philadelphia 🗞️, Chicago 🌆,
          Montreal 🍁, and Toronto 🚀.
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <ChangelogEntry month="April">
        <p>
          Visited Puerto Rico 🇵🇷 for a LeadSimple offsite. Spent a week in the
          east coast, 3 days in San Juan, and 3 days in Rincón on the West
          Coast.
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <ChangelogEntry month="February">
        <p>
          My 24th birthday 🎂. Spent a week in Punta del Este 🇺🇾 and a week in
          Curaçao 🇨🇼 with my girlfriend. The Carribean Sea is really one of a
          kind, can't wait to go back.
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <!-- =========== 2023 =========== -->
      <ChangelogEntry year={2023} month="December">
        <p>
          Attended the <Link href="https://www.leadsimple.com">LeadSimple</Link>
          user conference in Austin, Texas 🇺🇸. This was my first time speaking in
          English to a crowd. I was extremely nervous and couldn't stop shaking,
          but it went extremely well, it was a highlight of the year.
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <ChangelogEntry month="April">
        <p>
          First time in the US for the first LeadSimple off-site in Austin,
          Texas 🇺🇸.
        </p>
        <p>
          Went to Florida for the first time! Loved Disney World 🎢, Miami and
          Key West 🌴.
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <!-- =========== 2022 =========== -->
      <ChangelogEntry year={2022} month="July">
        <p>Aura 😻 joined our lives.</p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <ChangelogEntry month="June">
        <p>Graduated in Computer Science 🎓 <i>summa cum laude</i></p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <ChangelogEntry month="April">
        <p>
          Moved 🏠 back to Porto Alegre 🇧🇷 with my now-fiancée-then-girlfriend.
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <ChangelogEntry month="January">
        <p>
          Came back to Brazil 🇧🇷 after an exchange year in Germany 🇩🇪. Spent 4
          months living at the beach 🌴.
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <!-- =========== 2021 =========== -->
      <ChangelogEntry year={2021} month="December">
        <p>
          Lili came to visit me in Europe and we toured around Portugal 🇵🇹 and
          Spain 🇪🇸.
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <ChangelogEntry month="September">
        <p>Visited some friends studying in Grenoble 🇫🇷.</p>
        <p>Visited Luxembourg 🇱🇺 with a couple of German friends.</p>
        <p>
          My first trip totally on my own. Visited Switzerland 🇨🇭 albeit only
          for a single day.
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <ChangelogEntry month="July">
        <p>
          Visited one of my best friends in the Balearic Islands 🇪🇸. Also spent
          some time in Barcelona.
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <ChangelogEntry month="March">
        <p>
          Moved to Germany 🇩🇪 for an exchange year at the Technische Universität
          Kaiserslautern (TUK).
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <ChangelogEntry month="February">
        <p>
          Started working at <Link href="https://leadsimple.com"
            >LeadSimple</Link
          > 🏠.
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <!-- =========== 2020 =========== -->
      <ChangelogEntry year={2020} month="March">
        <p>March 15th, 2020. The world changed. 🦠</p>
        <p>I moved back to my home town with my parents and younger brother.</p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <!-- =========== 2019 =========== -->
      <ChangelogEntry year={2019} month="September">
        <p>
          Started working at <Link href="https://site.taglivros.com"
            >Tag Livros</Link
          > 📚.
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <!-- =========== 2017 =========== -->
      <ChangelogEntry year={2017} month="July">
        <p>
          Started studying Computer Science at the <Link
            href="https://www.ufrgs.br"
            >Federal University of Rio Grande do Sul</Link
          >
          (UFRGS) 🇧🇷 🚌.
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <!-- =========== 2015 =========== -->
      <ChangelogEntry year={2015} month="December">
        <p>Started dating my now-fiancée, Lili 🌹.</p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <!-- =========== 2000 =========== -->
      <ChangelogEntry year={2000} month="February">
        <p>👶🏻🍼</p>
      </ChangelogEntry>
    </main>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .changelog {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  img .hero-image {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .last-updated-note {
    text-align: right;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--gray-400);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (min-width: 50em) {
    .changelog {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 60% 1fr;
    }

    .changelog > :global(:first-child) {
      grid-column-start: 3;
    }
  }
</style>
